### GeoRide Backend API Testing

### Get nearby drivers
GET http://localhost:5000/rider/nearby-drivers?lat=28.6140&lng=77.2091

### Request ride
POST http://localhost:5000/ride/request
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "riderId": "r_demo",
  "pickupLat": 28.6139,
  "pickupLng": 77.2090,
  "dropLat": 28.6200,
  "dropLng": 77.2200
}

### Get current rider ride
GET http://localhost:5000/ride/current?riderId=r_demo

### Get driver ride
GET http://localhost:5000/ride/driver?driverId=d_demo

### Verify ride OTP
POST http://localhost:5000/ride/verify-otp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "riderId": "r_demo",
  "otp": "1234"
}

### End ride
POST http://localhost:5000/ride/end
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "riderId": "r_demo"
}

### Cancel ride
POST http://localhost:5000/ride/cancel
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "riderId": "r_demo"
}

### Demand map
GET http://localhost:5000/admin/demand

### Hotspots
GET http://localhost:5000/admin/hotspots

### Recommendations
GET http://localhost:5000/admin/recommendations
